title: 2012 O'NEILL Superfreak Wetsuit
description: After the success of the F.U.Z.E. entry in the Psycho RG8 series, O'Neill's Area 52 team incorporated the same entry for our new SuperFreak series. With GBS seam construction and a super-flexible combination of UltraFlex DS and FluidFlex materials, the SuperFreak keeps the water out and keeps you warm like no other wetsuit ever offered at this price level.
